08:29.026 --> 08:32.174
Kenny's estranged ex, Mimi Waxberg!

08:32.176 --> 08:33.985
I'm sorry. What?

08:33.986 --> 08:35.075
Okay. You two, come on.

08:35.076 --> 08:37.106
Let's jump up and do the wedding scene.

08:41.046 --> 08:44.065
Okay, you know, zombies are one thing,

08:44.066 --> 08:46.095
but there is no wedding
scene in "Romeo and Juliet."

08:46.096 --> 08:48.105
I know. The whole
thing happened offstage.

08:48.106 --> 08:51.075
Shakespeare really left a
lot of meat on that bone.

08:51.076 --> 08:53.115
And no offense, Ms. Hanson,

08:53.116 --> 08:55.065
but this is worse than
when that harlot from "girls"

08:55.066 --> 08:56.145
played Peter Pan.

08:56.146 --> 08:59.196
♪ ♪

09:07.166 --> 09:09.015
[Clears throat]

09:09.016 --> 09:12.185
I, Romeo, take you, Juliet,

09:12.186 --> 09:15.095
