09:25.939 --> 09:28.858
all the "Romeo and Juliet" movies
tonight for inspiration.

09:28.859 --> 09:32.838
Um, actually, I'm all
good. I have seen them all.

09:32.839 --> 09:34.808
Even "Gnomeo and Juliet"?

09:34.809 --> 09:36.818
Oh, no. I missed that one.

09:36.819 --> 09:37.958
- I'll bring the snacks!
- Fantastic.

09:37.959 --> 09:40.818
Man: Come on, guys. We
don't have that much time.

09:40.819 --> 09:41.888
God, it's like the whole budget's

09:41.889 --> 09:42.928
going into the wedding scene,

09:42.929 --> 09:44.798
but I have to beg for decent stage blood

09:44.799 --> 09:45.878
for my blood cannon.

09:45.879 --> 09:48.828
Sure, I could go to the
dumpster behind the butcher shop,

09:48.829 --> 09:50.838
but I don't think anyone wants that.

09:50.839 --> 09:52.838
What? N-no.

09:52.839 --> 09:54.898
There are more important
things than your blood cannon.

09:54.899 --> 09:56.111
- These?
- Oh, the color

09:56.136 --> 09:57.808
scheme is ivory and rose,

09:57.809 --> 09:59.828
not champagne and bubble gum.

09:59.829 --> 10:01.858
- Get your head in the game, Lacey.
- Uh-huh.

10:01.859 --> 10:02.808
Mom?

10:02.809 --> 10:04.758
Yeah? Hi.

10:04.759 --> 10:06.858
Um, so, Mimi's starting to get

10:06.859 --> 10:08.798
